# CODEOWNERS
#
# HnsX uses GitHub's CODEOWNERS file to auto-request review from the
# right maintainer(s) when a PR touches a given area. The last matching
# rule wins, so put the most specific paths first.
#
# Format: <pattern>  <owner1>  <owner2> ...
# Owners must be GitHub usernames or team names (e.g. @narcilee7 or
# @hnsx-io/core).
#
# Until we grow enough active maintainers to staff per-area teams,
# everything below routes to the core team. As reviewers specialize,
# replace @hnsx-io/core with the relevant team or individual.

# Default owner for anything not matched below.
/                                          @narcilee7

